---
title: Herby Pork Meatballs & Zesty Freekeh with Broccoli & Honey Yoghurt
description: Freekeh becomes irresistible when there’s a zap of lemon tossed through. It also goes nicely with plump pork
meatballs to create a hearty meal in a bowl. These meatballs have a few tricks of their own like being seasoned with
herbs and drizzled in a sweetened honey yoghurt. There’s something new in every bite.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
